trans-unit.source: Safe — Enables the safe language dialect, asking GHC to guarantee trust. The safe language dialect requires that all imports be trusted or a compilation error will occur. Safe Haskell will also infer this safety type for modules automatically when possible. Please refer to section Safe Haskell Inference for more details of this.
trans-unit.target: Safe -启用安全语言方言，要求GHC保证信任。安全语言方言要求所有导入均受信任，否则将发生编译错误。Safe Haskell还将在可能时自动为模块推断此安全类型。有关更多详细信息，请参阅“安全Haskell推论”部分。
-XStandaloneDeriving （请参阅独立派生声明）

trans-unit.source: Trustworthy — Means that while this module may invoke unsafe functions internally, the module’s author claims that it exports an API that can’t be used in an unsafe way. This doesn’t enable the safe language. It does however restrict the resolution of overlapping instances to only allow safe overlapping instances. The trust guarantee is provided by the module author, not GHC. An import statement with the safe keyword results in a compilation error if the imported module is not trusted. An import statement without the keyword behaves as usual and can import any module whether trusted or not.
trans-unit.target: Trustworthy -表示虽然此模块可能在内部调用不安全的函数，但该模块的作者声称它导出了不能以不安全的方式使用的API。这不会启用安全语言。但是，它确实限制了重叠实例的分辨率，只允许安全重叠实例。信任保证由模块作者而非GHC提供。如果导入的模块不受信任，则带有 safe 关键字的import语句会导致编译错误。不带关键字的import语句的行为与往常一样，并且可以导入任何模块（无论是否受信任）。

trans-unit.source: Unsafe — Marks the module being compiled as unsafe so that modules compiled using Safe can’t import it. You may want to explicitly mark a module unsafe when it exports internal constructors that can be used to violate invariants.
trans-unit.target: Unsafe -将要编译的模块标记为不安全，以使使用“ Safe 编译的模块无法导入。您可能想在模块导出内部构造函数时显式标记为不安全，该内部构造函数可用于违反不变式。

:def is used to define new commands, or macros, in GHCi. The command :def ⟨name⟩ ⟨expr⟩ defines a new GHCi command :name, implemented by the Haskell expression ⟨expr⟩, which must have type String -> IO String. When :name args is typed at the prompt, GHCi will run the expression (name args), take the resulting String, and feed it back into GHCi as a new sequence of commands. Separate commands in the result must be separated by “\n”.
trans-unit.target: :def 用于在GHCi中定义新命令或宏。命令 :def ⟨name⟩ ⟨expr⟩ 定义了一个新的GHCi命令 :name ，由Haskell表达式⟨expr⟩实现，其类型必须为String- String -> IO String 。在提示符下键入 :name args 时，GHCi将运行表达式 (name args) ，获取结果 String ，并将其作为新的命令序列反馈给GHCi。结果中的单独命令必须用“ \n ”分隔。
